{"tid":157830,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［時代變］其實依家啲細路係咪唔會再追卡通片？","createTime":"2017-03-15T20:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T21:10:44.000Z","uid":5190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9626479f28ddb27c58aa2446a0673f61653bf26e","tid":157830,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T20:18:10.000Z","msg":"90後個個都大個晒啦 毛都生齊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家科技日新月異 個個細路都有一部手機 無手機都有遊戲機啦 邊似我地以之前淨係得電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個一放學就返屋企開電視追卡通 返學校就傾劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲記得個鐘意pokemon到一個地步係幻想自己身邊有隻Pokemon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家 連名都比人搞到成舊屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1E6O2Sh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1E6O2Sh.jpg&h=59b6d9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有pokemon 點少得數碼暴龍呀 以前成日去表哥屋企打ps隻數碼暴龍game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出左數碼暴龍機又係咁求老母買 同同學鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班友仔都大個晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/040151_01d3e43b7f8aec6dc8517716d5945179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F040151_01d3e43b7f8aec6dc8517716d5945179.jpg&h=4f690562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/040739_a7d57d235cae32023143a852e6cfeda3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F040739_a7d57d235cae32023143a852e6cfeda3.jpg&h=15df6801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKeroro又係一套人人都鐘意嘅卡通片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5個深入小朋友心嘅外星人想侵略地球 真係又愛又恨佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2576P3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2576P3s.jpg&h=2949d805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動物橫町依套唔講唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係主題曲主唱嘉欣bb已經不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 套野到我大個都仲係咁鐘意<br />\n<br />\n依家 鐘嘉欣連仔都生埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Lb52CH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Lb52CH.jpg&h=50a7d3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n足球小將依太熱血野點可以唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然啲角色身體構造有啲離地 對腳長到仆街 但套野一講 有邊個會未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沖力射球 一技 有邊個未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z73aoN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ73aoN8.jpg&h=48f12c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多套卡通片都想講 但我想講嘅係 你大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真 依家啲卡通片真係十舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d134c62beda09eb405ac74f3d4781025f5ed05a7","tid":157830,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T20:24:40.000Z","msg":"仲有特攝片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加啲卡通片好兒童向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ddfde96494e31f6aa070ccf5a4c3f4e476d605","tid":157830,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T20:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有特攝片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加啲卡通片好兒童向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見撚到3d我都笑撚左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8093bd7c7904f0a123db9eff27cb54ee7d05476","tid":157830,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T20:37:43.000Z","msg":"神你老母奇寶貝咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3451e42030cfe21fb518a00fe9fd852d405392cd","tid":157830,"uid":5724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:10:44.000Z","msg":"細個睇IQ博士同亂太郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:90後，但呀媽成日俾佢細個睇嗰啲卡通我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}